Life is good for Nino van Doorn (8). He has a terrific brother Lucas (14), 
wise father Bruno and an angel of a mother, Marla. When Marla dies, 
Bruno can't cope with her death. Also the values like order, responsibility, 
love and care they represented. The two brothers create their own world. 
But soon the anarchistic world is threatened by the outside world. The two 
brothers are prepared to fool the system but what happens is that they really
 become a family again. 


